{"tid":653070,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"楊潤雄與眾志公開討論教科書爭議   局長：「係咪對你哋思想咁大影響？","createTime":"2018-05-04T11:09:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-05T07:06:30.000Z","uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"afe7eb0abce5f39a11d35d8353479a5e361be273","tid":653070,"uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T11:09:52.000Z","msg":"教育局局長楊潤雄到一間中學出席活動中途，到學校門外與向他請願的眾志成員直接對話，雙方談到歷史教科書評審爭議。<br />\n<br />\n楊潤雄表示，評審小組見到教科書用字不恰當，提出疑問並無問題，又反問眾志成員都是讀這些教科書長大，是否對大家思想有大影響，可各自評論。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/icablenews/videos/842064509318952/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ficablenews%2Fvideos%2F842064509318952%2F&d=NgQhf2UES2tGDLRuWrIPWwCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=8b6e6437\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/icablenews/videos/842064509318952/</a>"},{"pid":"73ee1ee9be37611444d80d9e6bb582d44e474ad7","tid":653070,"uid":2419,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T11:12:28.000Z","msg":"發爛渣咁款<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fffe46bab07423bed995e1911675780a4bd0aaf","tid":653070,"uid":53687,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T11:32:36.000Z","msg":"無影響你改嚟做乜？"},{"pid":"6029b44cca36756e52a716448c936c8f74e7de0f","tid":653070,"uid":31,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T11:34:18.000Z","msg":"好撚肉酸 局長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fa3c02d14ac3cd5451716d71327c59fabd9989e","tid":653070,"uid":34785,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T11:52:53.000Z","msg":"佢敢直接對話，總算係無咁狗的狗官"},{"pid":"984e3b8763d44c192fcc8ff57edab15e0dcd655b","tid":653070,"uid":6752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T11:56:08.000Z","msg":"咁你改黎做乜?"},{"pid":"4729abd887fc430987c3349e9d3fdea72b73cb48","tid":653070,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime